news.title: First phase of Mumbai's metro line three to be commissioned soon
news.para: Addressing a press conference, Ashwini Bhide, managing director for Mumbai Metro Rail Corporation (MMRC), said the Metro Line 3 is poised to be commissioned very soon, subject to clearance by the Commissioner of Metro Railway Safety (CMRS).

news.title: Britain's NewRiver REIT to buy Capital & Regional in $196 million deal
news.para: The deal comes at a time of stabilising property values in the British commercial property sector and increased deal-making activity on the back of improved rental growth prospects.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh's industrial authorities to adopt standard building bylaws
news.para: Tasked with the responsibility of allocating land parcels to investors, the department of infrastructure and industrial development is carrying out works through eight different industrial development authorities involved with the process of aggregating and developing large land tracts across the state.
